{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be corporate and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureSphere Cyber Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #004085;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #b3d1ff;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #0056b3;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            border-bottom: none;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .services-list, .contact-info {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .services-list ul, .contact-info ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .services-list li, .contact-info li {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .services-list li::before {\n            content: \"\\2022\";\n            color: #007bff;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 1em;\n            margin-left: -1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 120px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #007bff;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureSphere Cyber Solutions</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Protecting Your Digital Future</h2>\n        <p>Expert cybersecurity services for a rapidly evolving threat landscape. We provide robust solutions to safeguard your data and infrastructure.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-list\">\n                <ul>\n                    <li><strong>Risk Assessment & Management:</strong> Identify and mitigate potential cyber threats before they impact your business.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Network Security:</strong> Fortify your network infrastructure with advanced protection measures.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Data Protection & Privacy:</strong> Ensure compliance and secure sensitive information against breaches.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Incident Response:</strong> Rapid and effective response to security incidents to minimize damage.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Security Awareness Training:</strong> Empower your employees to be the first line of defense.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>SecureSphere Cyber Solutions is a leading provider of comprehensive cybersecurity services. Our team of seasoned professionals is dedicated to delivering cutting-edge solutions tailored to meet the unique needs of your organization. We believe in a proactive approach to security, ensuring your business stays resilient against the latest cyber threats.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-form\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Let us help you build a more secure future. Contact us today for a consultation.</p>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureSphere Cyber Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}